# Popup / Modal

Component: `src/app/components/Popup.tsx`

## Container
- `bg-white w-[620px] max-h-[90vh] rounded-[4px] overflow-hidden`
- Centered in viewport

## Overlay
- Strong: `bg-[#101010]/70`
- Weak: `bg-[#101010]/13`

## Close Button
- `size-8 rounded-[4px] hover:bg-[#f5f9fe]`
- Icon: `size-6 text-[#101010]`

## Title
- `text-[32px] font-bold leading-[36px] text-[#101010]`

## Subtext
- `text-[14px] leading-[20px] text-[#101010]`

## Content Area
- Padding: `px-8`
- Gap: `gap-8` between sections

## Footer Bar
- Sky blue strip: `#00b8f5` (8px height)
- Navy strip: `#012a72` (8px height)
- Full width at bottom

## Types
| Type | Layout | Close Button |
|---|---|---|
| `status` | centered content | yes |
| `form` | left-aligned fields | yes |
| `loader` | centered spinner | no, auto-dismisses |
| `share` | share options | yes |

## Form Popup Fields
- Uses `PopupInput` which wraps `TextField` internally
- Maintains external API compatibility
